reviews.reviewText: It exactly fits my5300 winix for nearly half of what they charge for their filters. looks like they are the exact same, can't say if there is any difference in the quality of the materials, but by eye, they are identical.

reviews.name: Fellowes HF-300 True HEPA Filter
reviews.reviewText: Excellent quality product. Compares to other brands that cost a lot more. Fits perfectly on other model air cleaners.

reviews.name: Fellowes HF-300 True HEPA Filter
reviews.reviewText: I purchased these Hepa Filters for my Winnix PlasmaWave 5300 and they fit like a glove. I thought wow am I dreaming. This is a good price $68.97 for 3 filter sets and they fit my unit. Absolutely happy person with this product.
